data.description:
Sitting on almost 3/4 of an acre, this 4 bedroom 2.5 Bath home features hardwood floors, dining area open to the kitchen, a jetted pool and tray ceiling in the master suite, 2 car garage, a deck overlooking an amazing yard w/ a fire pit, and built-in shelving that adds a touch of elegance to the Great Room. Just painted and carpet professionally cleaned.

Tenant responsible for all utilities and lawn care.
Dogs negotiable on individual basis with nonrefundable deposit.
